'''小詹姆斯·布莱恩·科米'''（{{lang-en|James Brien Comey, Jr.}}，{{bd|1960年|12月14日}}），第七任[[美国联邦调查局|美国联邦调查局]]-{局}-长，由[[巴拉克·奧巴馬|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]提名，自2013年9月4日起就任，2017年5月9日被[[美国总统|总统]][[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]終止職務。

他被指在[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]]期間涉入调查[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]的[[希拉里·克林顿电子邮件争议|电郵争议]]，他的决定被许多分析者（包括[[FiveThirtyEight|FiveThirtyEight]]的[[納特·西爾弗|納特·西爾弗]]）指称可能影響了最終的選舉结果。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/the-comey-letter-probably-cost-clinton-the-election/ |title=The Comey Letter Probably Cost Clinton The Election |last=Silver |first=Nate |date=May 3, 2017 |website=[[FiveThirtyEight|FiveThirtyEight]] |access-date=May 3, 2017 |archive-date=2021-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505075301/http://fivethirtyeight.com/features/the-comey-letter-probably-cost-clinton-the-election/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vox.com/the-big-idea/2017/1/11/14215930/comey-email-election-clinton-campaign|title=4 pieces of evidence showing FBI Director James Comey cost Clinton the election|access-date=2017-05-17|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316231528/https://www.vox.com/the-big-idea/2017/1/11/14215930/comey-email-election-clinton-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2017/02/james-comey-fbi-director-letter|title=The True Story of the Comey Letter Debacle|first=Bethany|last=McLean|access-date=2017-05-17|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123025553/https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2017/02/james-comey-fbi-director-letter|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

科米在2017年5月9日被总统特朗普[[詹姆斯·科米免職事件|免职]]，据称就在科米请求从[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]为联邦调查局对[[2016年俄羅斯干預美國選舉|2016年俄羅斯干預美國選舉]]的调查获取更多资源的几天后；司法部称《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》报道科米请求更多经费“完全是虚假的”。<ref name="BREAKING: White House announces President Donald Trump has fired FBI Director James Comey">{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fbi-director-james-comey-fired/story?id=47309009|title=FBI Director Comey fired amid Russia probe|first1=Jonathan|last1=Karl|first2=Meghan|last2=Keneally|first3=Justin|last3=Fishel|work=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|date=May 9, 2017|accessdate=May 11, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226160422/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/fbi-director-james-comey-fired/story?id=47309009|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NYT11may17>{{cite news|last1=[[Matthew_Rosenberg|Matthew Rosenberg]]|last2=[[Matt_Apuzzo|Matt Apuzzo]]|title=F.B.I. FIRING ROILS CAPITAL AS TRUMP CALLS OUT CRITICS – In Last Days as Chief, Comey Sought Aid in Russia Inquiry|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/10/us/politics/comey-russia-investigation-fbi.html|accessdate=May 11, 2017|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=May 11, 2017|page=A1|archive-date=2017-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170514213607/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/10/us/politics/comey-russia-investigation-fbi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Funding Request Denial">{{cite web|url=http://www.roanoke.com/washingtonpost/uncategorized/justice-department-denies-report-comey-requested-more-funding-for-russia/article_26697e47-78d9-5448-bfcb-935970310855.html|title=Justice Department denies report Comey requested more funding for Russia probe|accessdate=May 11, 2017|archive-date=2017-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511050713/http://www.roanoke.com/washingtonpost/uncategorized/justice-department-denies-report-comey-requested-more-funding-for-russia/article_26697e47-78d9-5448-bfcb-935970310855.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="DoJ denies request">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2017/05/10/comey-reportedly-asked-for-more-money-for-russia-probe-doj-calls-reports-totally-false.html|title=Comey reportedly asked for more resources for Russia probe; DOJ calls reports 'totally false'|last=Wang|first=Christine|work=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|accessdate=May 11, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223043546/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/05/10/comey-reportedly-asked-for-more-money-for-russia-probe-doj-calls-reports-totally-false.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>白宫发布的一份声明称移除科米将有助于结束俄罗斯有关调查。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/05/11/politics/comey-fbi-investigation-russia-sarah-huckabee-sanders/index.html|title=White House: Removing Comey will help bring Russia investigation to end|last=Producer|first=Kevin Liptak, CNN White House|website=CNN|access-date=May 11, 2017|archive-date=2017-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511234525/http://www.cnn.com/2017/05/11/politics/comey-fbi-investigation-russia-sarah-huckabee-sanders/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>其后，特朗普在接受[[NBC新闻|NBC新闻]]采访时表示，當他做出此決定時思考著“這個[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]與特朗普和俄羅斯的事情是一個編造的故事，這是[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨人]]失去了應該贏得選舉的藉口。”<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barrett|first1=Devlin|last2=Rucker|first2=Philip|title=Trump said he was thinking of Russia controversy when he decided to fire Comey|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/trump-says-fbi-director-comey-told-him-three-times-he-wasnt-under-investigation-once-in-a-phone-call-initiated-by-the-president/2017/05/11/2b384c9a-3669-11e7-b4ee-434b6d506b37_story.html?hpid=hp_hp-top-table-main_trumpcomey-120pm%3Ahomepage%2Fstory&utm_term=.e84bb8dc6943|website=Washington Post|accessdate=12 May 2017|archive-date=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726104029/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/trump-says-fbi-director-comey-told-him-three-times-he-wasnt-under-investigation-once-in-a-phone-call-initiated-by-the-president/2017/05/11/2b384c9a-3669-11e7-b4ee-434b6d506b37_story.html?hpid=hp_hp-top-table-main_trumpcomey-120pm%3Ahomepage%2Fstory&utm_term=.e84bb8dc6943|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根据一份科米的{{le|科米备忘录|Comey memos|个人备忘录}}，特朗普要求他个人终止对[[迈克尔·T·弗林|迈克尔·T·弗林将军]]与外国政府利益关系的调查。这份备忘录也称特朗普要求监禁某些特定的记者。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://thehill.com/homenews/news/333746-press-freedom-group-rips-trump-for-suggesting-comey-jail-reporters|title=Press freedom group rips Trump for suggesting Comey jail reporters|last=Firozi|first=Paulina|date=2017-05-16|work=TheHill|access-date=2017-05-17|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226050050/https://thehill.com/homenews/news/333746-press-freedom-group-rips-trump-for-suggesting-comey-jail-reporters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/16/us/politics/james-comey-trump-flynn-russia-investigation.html|title=Comey Memo Says Trump Asked Him to End Flynn Investigation|last=Schmidt|first=Michael S.|date=2017-05-16|work=The New York Times|access-date=2017-05-17|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170516212935/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/16/us/politics/james-comey-trump-flynn-russia-investigation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

值得一提的是，科米身高6呎8吋（約203cm），在政界、法律界極罕見，故在記者會和會議非常惹注目。

== 早年 ==
他生于[[纽约州|纽约州]][[扬克斯_(纽约州)|扬克斯]]，成长于[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]的Allendale<ref>McCaffrey, Shannon. [http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2003/12/14/for_new_deputy_attorney_general_a_department_under_fire/ "For new deputy attorney general, a department under fire"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2003/12/14/for_new_deputy_attorney_general_a_department_under_fire/ |date=20160304212301 }}, ''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]'', December 14, 2003. Accessed August 21, 2011. "As a teenager, he got a frightening taste of what it's like to be a crime victim when an intruder broke into his home in Allendale, N. J., while his parents were out and held his brother and him hostage at gunpoint. The captor fled and never was apprehended."</ref><ref>Weiser, Benjamin. [http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/02/nyregion/man-in-the-news-reputation-for-tenacity-james-brien-comey.html?pagewanted=all "Man in the News; Reputation for Tenacity; James Brien Comey"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/02/nyregion/man-in-the-news-reputation-for-tenacity-james-brien-comey.html?pagewanted=all |date=20181230061312 }}, ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'', December 2, 2011. Accessed August 21, 2011. "EDUCATION: Northern Highlands Regional High School, Allendale, N.J.; B.S., College of William and Mary; J.D., University of Chicago Law School."</ref>。1982年毕业于[[威廉与玛丽学院|威廉与玛丽学院]]的[[化学|化学]]、[[宗教|宗教]]专业<ref>[http://nymag.com/nymetro/news/politics/n_9353/ "Mr. Comey Goes To Washington"] {{Wayback|url=http://nymag.com/nymetro/news/politics/n_9353/ |date=20170518223645 }}, ''New York'' magazine, October 2003. Retrieved May 21, 2007.</ref>。1985年取得[[芝加哥大学法学院|芝加哥大学法学院]]的[[法律博士|法律博士]]学位。

法学院毕业后，他担任美国[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]地区法官{{Link-en|小約翰·沃克|John M. Walker, Jr.}}的法官助理。1987年进入美国司法部，1993年以前在纽约南区检察院工作。

1996年到2001年，他负责[[美国弗吉尼亚东区联邦地区法院|弗吉尼亚东区联邦地区法院]][[里奇蒙_(維吉尼亞州)|里士满]]管辖地区的检察起诉事宜。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/01/opinion/a-worthy-new-york-prosecutor.html "a-worthy-new-york-prosecutor"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/01/opinion/a-worthy-new-york-prosecutor.html |date=20210127220717 }}, [[Op-ed|Op-ed]], New York ''Times'', 2001/12/01.</ref>同时还担任[[里士满大学|里士满大学]]法学院的兼职教授<ref name="comeywh"/>。

== 職業生涯 ==
[[File:White-House-Fires-James-Comey.pdf|thumb]]
[[File:2017-05-16-JEC-to-McCabe-FBI-Memos.pdf|thumb]]{{tsl|en|United States House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform|监督委员会}}主席[[杰森·查菲茨|杰森·查菲茨]]在写给[[聯邦調查局長|联邦调查局代理局长]][[安德魯·G·麥卡比|安德魯·G·麥卡比]]的信中要求获取{{le|科米备忘录|Comey memos|科米备忘录}}内容]]

2002年1月到2003年12月，科米担任[[纽约南区|纽约南区]]检察院[[检察官|检察官]]<ref name="comeywh">[http://georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/government/comey-bio.html Deputy Attorney General James B. Comey] {{Wayback|url=http://georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/government/comey-bio.html |date=20170916132053 }} ''The White House.'' (no date). Retrieved May 18, 2007.</ref>，这是美国司法系统中最重要的起诉机关之一，是美国打击[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]、企业违法、[[毒品|毒品]]交易和有组织犯罪的前沿阵地。<ref name="就职">{{cite web |url=http://news.163.com/13/0905/10/980K855I00014JB6.html |language= |title=美新任FBI局长宣誓就职 曾任美司法部副部长 |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2013-09-05 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180414091658/http://news.163.com/13/0905/10/980K855I00014JB6.html |archive-date=2018-04-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2003年12月到2005年8月，科米曾任[[小布什|小布什]]政府司法部副部长。任期内他领导了司法部反欺诈特别小组，并促成在20个城市建立“暴力犯罪影响组”，调查与[[枪支|枪支]]相关的犯罪。<ref name="就职"/>

2005年8月以后，他成为[[洛克希德·马丁|洛克希德·马丁]]公司的法律总顾问。2010年他成为{{Link-en|橋水聯合|Bridgewater Associates|橋水聯合對沖基金}}的法律总顾问。2013年初，他离开该公司担任[[哥伦比亚大学法学院|哥伦比亚大学法学院]]国家安全法方面的高级研究学者。他也是英国[[汇丰控股有限公司|汇丰控股有限公司]]的董事会成员。

2013年6月，他經总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]提名为新一任联邦调查局（FBI）-{局}-长<ref>Pickler, Nedra, [http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_23510972/obamas-fbi-pick-james-comey-challenged-wiretapping-by "Obama's FBI pick: James Comey, challenged wiretapping by Bush White House"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/nation-world/ci_23510972/obamas-fbi-pick-james-comey-challenged-wiretapping-by |date=20160401215438 }}, AP via ''mercurynews.com'', June 21, 2013. Retrieved 2013-06-21.</ref>。同年9月4日，正式接替任职达12年的[[羅伯特·穆勒|穆勒]]，担任联邦调查局第七任-{局}-长。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fbi.gov/news/news_blog/james-b.-comey-sworn-in-as-fbi-director |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715003956/http://www.fbi.gov/news/news_blog/james-b.-comey-sworn-in-as-fbi-director |archivedate=2014-07-15 }}</ref>

2016年10月28日，距離[[2016年美國總統選舉|美國總統選舉]]不到10天，科米寫信給國會說要重啟[[希拉蕊·柯林頓|希拉蕊·柯林頓]]的[[希拉蕊·柯林頓電子郵件爭議|電郵門]]事件調查，並表示在跟電郵門不相關的調查行動中發現一批希拉蕊掌國務院時期電郵，準備審核是否涉機密資料，外界質疑此舉是為了影響選情，曾經是[[美国共和党|共和党]]員的FBI局長科米自清，他已經放棄共和黨籍，強調FBI絕對中立。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/683584 |title=美FBI選前用奧步？　局長自清：已非共和黨員 |access-date=2016-11-03 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104021952/http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/683584 |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月7日，科米再次致函國會表示已對早前發現的一批電郵完成審核維持不起訴決定<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/first/20161108/19826417 |title=局長再函國會 極速查完新電郵　FBI：不起訴希拉莉 |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2016-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111071650/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/first/20161108/19826417 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，FBI解釋是因為檢視了前國會議員[[安东尼·韦纳|安东尼·韦纳]]的信箱後發現裡面數千封的電子郵件都是私人或是之前已經被調查過的重複信件，沒有發現希拉蕊的機密郵件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/684971 |title=FOCUS／解套！最後48小時　FBI局長：電郵無罪 |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2016-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111094236/http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/684971 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年5月，柯米被美国总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]無預警[[詹姆斯·科米免職事件|解除FBI局長职位]]，这是美國史上第二次FBI局長被开除，引發了[[川普外流訊息給俄羅斯事件|通俄門]]事件發酵。外界猜測與柯米開始調查川普當選過程有無俄羅斯干預有關，所以川普先下手為強，對此川普政府否認此說法。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-H5q_W6MATo |title=央視官方頻道-“通俄门”调查升温 |access-date=2017-05-13 |archive-date=2021-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715160852/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-H5q_W6MATo |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 离任后活动 ==
柯米在离任后将自己的备忘录以间接方式公开，这些备忘录直接促使了美国司法部副部长罗宾斯坦聘请特别检察官[[羅伯特·穆勒|穆勒]]调查特朗普团队竞选期间的行为。

2018年上半年，柯米作成《{{le|更高的忠誠：真相、謊言和領導|A Higher Loyalty}}》（'''''A Higher Loyalty: Truth, Lies, and Leadership'''''）一書，详述自己职业生涯和2016年自己作出各种调查决定的原因。

2018年秋季，柯米在母校威廉玛丽学院担任教授。

==个人生活==
他与妻子Patrice育有5个子女。之前他是共和党成员，曾支持参议员[[約翰·麥凱恩|約翰·麥凱恩]]的[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年总统竞选活动]]，也曾支持州长[[米特·羅姆尼|米特·羅姆尼]]的[[2012年美国总统选举|2012年总统竞选]]。<ref>[http://www.politico.com/story/2013/05/james-comey-fbi-92010_Page2.html#ixzz2UkJwWwdL "james-comey-fbi"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2013/05/james-comey-fbi-92010_Page2.html#ixzz2UkJwWwdL |date=20181230122402 }}, ''politico.com'', 2013/05.</ref>

